---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../site.config';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Mould Inspection London | Black Mould Investigation | IBSF"
  description="Independent mould inspection London. Black mould investigation, condensation survey and indoor air quality testing. Forensic mould diagnostics for disputes and health complaints. IBSF."
>
  <article class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-navy sm:text-4xl">
      Mould inspection London
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-navy-muted leading-relaxed">
      Mould in London properties is frequently a symptom of ventilation failure, condensation or water ingressâ€”not simply a cleaning problem. A <strong>mould inspection London</strong> by IBSF identifies the root cause using instrument-led forensic diagnostics. We investigate <strong>black mould investigation London</strong>, condensation survey and indoor air quality testing to produce defensible reports for landlord-tenant disputes, insurance claims and health complaints.
    </p>
    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Why mould keeps coming back</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-navy-muted leading-relaxed">
      Cleaning mould without addressing the cause guarantees recurrence. Our forensic approach measures humidity, ventilation rates, dew point conditions and surface temperatures to isolate why mould is growing. We distinguish between condensation-driven mould and mould caused by water ingress or building defects.
    </p>
    <h2 class="mt-10 text-xl font-semibold text-navy">Coverage</h2>
    <p class="mt-2 text-navy-muted"><strong>Mould inspection London</strong>, <strong>mould inspection South East</strong> and Hampshire. Condensation survey London, damp survey Haringey, damp survey Camden, damp survey Southwark.</p>
    <section class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/contact" class="rounded bg-navy px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-white no-underline hover:bg-navy-light">Commission mould investigation</a>
      <a href="/services/damp-moisture-forensics" class="rounded border-2 border-navy px-6 py-3 font-semibold text-navy no-underline hover:bg-navy hover:text-white">Damp & moisture forensics</a>
    </section>
    <p class="mt-8 border-t border-gray-200 pt-6 text-sm text-navy-muted"><strong>NAP:</strong> {siteConfig.name}, {siteConfig.address.full}. Tel: {siteConfig.phone}. Email: {siteConfig.email}.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
